      <title>Bookcase Layout Document</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/layouts/bookcase/docs/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/layouts/bookcase/docs/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Bookcase layout is useful for creating another viewpoint of list contents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This layout can only be used on section page (&lt;code&gt;_index.md&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Configuration&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;type&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;bookcase&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Specify &lt;code&gt;type&lt;/code&gt; in front-matter will change the template lookup order.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;bookcase_list_sections&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;List subsections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;bookcase_list_sections&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;default: true&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;bookcase_list_pages&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;List pages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;bookcase_list_pages&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;default: true&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Resouces Configuration&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;These parameters are located in bookcase item&amp;rsquo;s resource. For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;.
├── books.md &amp;lt;- config is located in here!
├── category
│   └── _index.md &amp;lt;- and here!
└── _index.md &amp;lt;- your bookcase layout
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;bookcase_cover_src&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The cover image URL relative to the base URL. (with or without &lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt; prefix)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
